u0111\u1ea5t kh\u00e1ch.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>M\u00f4ng lung gi\u1eefa chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00ecn v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/ket-qua-crystal-palace-vs-liverpool-tran-dau-vong-32-premier-league-201718-172-183225.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Crystal Palace vs Liverpool v\u00f2ng 32 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh</strong></span>, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a HLV Jurgen Klopp. To\u00e0n b\u1ed9 11 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 trong tay chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng tung ra s\u00e2n Selhurst Park. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Klopp mu\u1ed1n m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Man City t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Champions League sau \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt ng\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, ngh\u0129 bao gi\u1edd c\u0169ng d\u1ec5 h\u01a1n l\u00e0m. Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee9 d\u00e1m ngh\u0129, d\u00e1m l\u00e0m l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh hi\u1ec7n nay, nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh to\u00e1n c\u1ee7a Klopp b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf. C\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng khi b\u01b0\u1edbc ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft cao nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Crystal Palace vs Liverpool 90 phut nho doi cua Klopp hinh anh\" title=\"Crystal Palace vs Liverpool 90 ph\u00fat nh\u1edb \u0111\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Klopp h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/31/Crystal-Palace-vs-Liverpool-90-phut-nho-doi-cua-Klopp-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Crystal Palace vs Liverpool v\u00f2ng 32 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c ch\u1eadm</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n, Klopp \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. N\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, \u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1ecdi ra qu\u1edf tr\u00e1ch ho\u1eb7c th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 thay h\u1ecd ra. Nh\u01b0ng khi t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng tr\u00ean x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u00e1 t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Liverpool c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e0nh b\u00f3 tay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 c\u1ea3 Klopp. \u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh Liverpool b\u1ecb ph\u00e2n t\u00e2m b\u1edfi cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1edbi Man City gi\u1eefa tu\u1ea7n sau. V\u00f4 t\u00ecnh, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-crystal-palace-vs-liverpool-18h30-ngay-313-premier-league-201718-372-183214.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Crystal Palace vs Liverpool</strong></span> v\u00f2ng 32 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh tr\u1edf n\u00ean qu\u00e1 th\u1eeba th\u00e3i v\u1edbi h\u1ecd. Trong t\u00e2m tr\u00ed L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf b\u1ecb gi\u1eb1ng x\u00e9 gi\u1eefa chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palace hay d\u00e0nh s\u1ee9c cho Man City.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mane cua Liverpool co bong truoc Palace\" title=\"Mane cua Liverpool co bong truoc Palace\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/31/Mane-cua-Liverpool-co-bong-truoc-Palace.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mane v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ngh\u0129 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edbi Man City</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do trong ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Selhurst Park, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y l\u1eeda nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh n\u01a1i Liverpool ch\u00e1y m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7. C\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Palace trong th\u1ebf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafp l\u00ean ng\u1ecdn l\u1eeda c\u00f2n to h\u01a1n The Kop. \u0110\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch c\u00f2n cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1i quan tr\u1ecdng ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n ch\u00f9n ch\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc phong th\u00e1i kh\u00f4ng khoan nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 b\u1eebng t\u1ec9nh k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\nLiverpool mu\u1ed1n m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh. Ngay ph\u00fat 13, pha lao ra b\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p l\u00fd c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Loris Karius khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch v\u00f9ng Merseyside ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty. Tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, Luka Milivojevic kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Liverpool b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u1eeda sai n\u00e0o m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho Crystal Palace.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Milivojevic da penalty\" title=\"Milivojevic da penalty\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/31/Milivojevic-da-penalty.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Palace c\u00f2n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc sau c\u00fa ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Milivojevic</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, Liverpool l\u1ea5n c\u1ea5n gi\u1eefa chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 gi\u1eef s\u1ee9c su\u1ed1t m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i. Ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9, m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 kh\u00edch l\u1ec7 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Klopp, m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u0169ng k\u1ecbp b\u1eebng t\u1ec9nh sau hi\u1ec7p 1 nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a, \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch cho th\u1ea5y nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc. H\u1ecd l\u1ea5n \u00e1t Palace nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n v\u00e0 th\u1eadt may m\u1eafn l\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m n\u01a1i Palace. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 m\u00e1u l\u1eeda nh\u01b0ng tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i b\u00e0n th\u00eam. Khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u1ecbu s\u1ee9c \u00e9p t\u1edbi t\u1eeb d\u00e0n sao Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ec9nh gi\u1ea5c, l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Roy Hodgson l\u00fang t\u00fang. Hi\u1ec7p 2 l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i t\u1ea1i sao h\u1ecd th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi 48 b\u00e0n sau 31 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Crystal Palace vs Liverpool v\u00f2ng 32 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, con s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 t\u0103ng l\u00ean tr\u00f2n 50.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLiverpool ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n trong hi\u1ec7p 2 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t c\u00e1c ph\u00fat 49 v\u00e0 84 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u1eafng l\u1ea1i 2-1. \u1ede c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n thua, Palace \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed5ng c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 khai th\u00e1c. Liverpool ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng kho\u00e9t v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Aaron Wan-Bissaka m\u1edbi 20 tu\u1ed5i b\u00ean ph\u00eda ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Salah an dinh chien thang truoc Palace\" title=\"Salah an dinh chien thang truoc Palace\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/31/liverpool-vs-crystal-palace-vong-32-ngoai-hang-anh-90-phut-nho-doi-voi-the-klopp.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u1eadt may \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t James Milner v\u00e0 Andew Robertson \u0111\u00e3 tung ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n d\u1ecdn c\u1ed7 cho Sadio Mane v\u00e0 Mohamed Salah l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng. \u0110\u00f3 m\u1edbi l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Liverpool: Nhanh, m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n. Nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng th\u1eadt may l\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ecbp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi qu\u00e1 mu\u1ed9n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palace gi\u00fap Liverpool ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn b\u1ea3o to\u00e0n v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 tr\u00ean BXH gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh sau v\u00f2ng 32. H\u1ecd t\u1ea1m b\u1ecf c\u00e1ch v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 5 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 Champions League c\u1ee7a Chelsea tr\u00f2n 10 \u0111i\u1ec3m (ch\u01a1i h\u01a1n 2 tr\u1eadn) tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o derby gian kh\u00f3 v\u1edbi Tottenham t\u1ed1i ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt (1/4).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 l\u00e0 b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Klopp. H\u1ecd c\u1ea7n c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nghi\u00eam t\u00fac v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. \u0110\u00f4i khi, tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3\u2026<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH THI \u0110\u1ea4U<br>\r\nCrystal Palace: </strong>Hennessey, Wan-Bissaka (Fosu-Mensah 88'), Kelly, Sakho, Van Aanholt, Townsend, Cabaye (Loftus-Cheek 73'), McArthur, Milivojevic, Benteke, Zaha.<br>\r\n<strong>Liverpool: </strong>Karius, Alexander-Arnold, Matip, Van Dijk, Robertson, Wijnaldum (Lallana 65' (Lovren 70')), Henderson, Milner, Salah, Firmino, Mane (Oxlade-Chamberlain 64').<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Crystal Palace vs Liverpool\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Crystal Palace vs Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/31/Thong-tin-sau-tran-Crystal-Palace-vs-Liverpool.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Crystal Palace vs Liverpool <span id=\"ctl00_m_contentBody_sp_title\" class=\"sp_title\">v\u00f2ng 32 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh</span></h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Crystal Palace 1-2 Liverpool (v\u00f2ng 32 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2017/18):</strong><br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_264944\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/03/31/highlight-crystal-palace-vs-liverpool-vong-32-nha-full.mp4&autoplay=false\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Liverpool tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-crystal-palace-12-liverpool-vong-32-premier-league-201718-326-183239.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Crystal Palace 1-2 Liverpool (V\u00f2ng 32 Premier League 2017/18)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ket-qua-crystal-palace-vs-liverpool-tran-dau-vong-32-premier-league-201718-172-183225.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Crystal Palace vs Liverpool tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 32 Premier League 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-crystal-palace-vs-liverpool-18h30-ngay-313-premier-league-201718-372-183214.html\">Crystal Palace 1-2 Liverpool (KT): Si\u00eau Salah l\u1ea1i n\u1ed5 s\u00fang, The Kop th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tru-cot-liverpool-tro-lai-sau-10-thang-chan-thuong-172-183212.html\">Tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Liverpool tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau 10 th\u00e1ng d\u01b0\u1ee1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-ket-luan-chinh-thuc-ve-hau-ve-joe-gomez-chan-thuong-172-183165.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a sao Liverpool</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"654","checkdouble":"183242"},{"date":"21:54 31/03","title":"Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c n\u1ed5 s\u00fang, Salah c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Ronaldo v\u00e0 Van Persie","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/31/tiep-tuc-no-sung-salah-can-bang-ky-luc-cua-ronaldo-va-van-persie.JPG","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.a