padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Si\u00eau sao Mohamed Salah \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Ronaldo v\u00e0 Van Persie sau khi ghi b\u00e0n gi\u00fap Liverpool v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Crystal Palace \u1edf Selhurst Park.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tiep tuc no sung, Salah lap ky luc sau tran gap Palace hinh anh\" title=\"Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c n\u1ed5 s\u00fang, Salah l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Palace h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/31/tiep-tuc-no-sung-salah-can-bang-ky-luc-cua-ronaldo-va-van-persie.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Salah l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Crystal Palace</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mohamed Salah \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 t\u1eadm t\u1ecbt trong ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u1eddi gian tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Palace. Nh\u01b0ng trong m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u1edf ph\u00fat 84, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp nh\u01b0 t\u1eeb d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea5t chui l\u00ean trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba c\u1ee7a Crystal Palace. Anh kh\u1ed1ng ch\u1ebf b\u00f3ng b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tung c\u00fa s\u00fat ch\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i mang v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 chung cu\u1ed9c cho <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/liverpool-vs-crystal-palace-vong-32-ngoai-hang-anh-90-phut-nho-doi-voi-the-klopp-172-183242.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool</span>.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 29 c\u1ee7a Salah \u1edf Premier League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. V\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 Kevin De Bruyne c\u1ee7a Man City l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh duy nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m v\u1edbi Salah.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n3 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1eeba gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Crystal Palace kh\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Liverpool. V\u00e0 Salah c\u0169ng san b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 3 \u1edf Premier League khi ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf 21 trong 38 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c n\u00e0y \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2007/08. Van Persie c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o c\u1ee7a Man United m\u00f9a 2012/13. Nh\u01b0ng nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c n\u00e0y s\u1ebd s\u1edbm thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Salah. B\u1edfi t\u1eeb gi\u1edd t\u1edbi cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp c\u00f2n 6 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n trong nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-vs-crystal-palace-vong-32-ngoai-hang-anh-90-phut-nho-doi-voi-the-klopp-172-183242.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/31/liverpool-vs-crystal-palace-vong-32-ngoai-hang-anh-90-phut-nho-doi-voi-the-klopp.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-vs-crystal-palace-vong-32-ngoai-hang-anh-90-phut-nho-doi-voi-the-klopp-172-183242.html\">Crystal Palace 1-2 Liverpool: 90 ph\u00fat nh\u1edb \u0111\u1eddi v\u1edbi \u201cThe Klopp\u201d</span><br>\r\n<span>Nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh to\u00e1n sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a HLV Jurgen Klopp tr\u01b0\u1edbc Crystal Palace su\u00fdt khi\u1ebfn Liverpool s\u1ea3y ch\u00e2n tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t kh\u00e1ch.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n trong nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Salah c\u00f2n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Premier League. Nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang n\u1eafm gi\u1eef k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t \u0111ang l\u00e0 Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 Luis Suarez v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng 31 b\u00e0n. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, vi\u1ec7c ghi 3 b\u00e0n trong nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Salah c\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00e1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Liverpool v\u1eeba qua gi\u00fap h\u1ecd t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng Premier League. Nh\u01b0ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ngay sau \u0111\u00f3, Man United \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Swansea v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 an to\u00e0n l\u00e0 2-0 ngay trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t. V\u00ec v\u1eady, The Kop nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 sau v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (Bongda24h)</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"653","checkdo