{border-bottom-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 ph\u00e2n nh\u00f3m h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng t\u1ea1i Asian Cup 2019, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u L\u0110B\u0110 Th\u00e1i Lan ch\u1ec9 e ng\u1ea1i c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp t\u1edbi \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 trong tay danh s\u00e1ch 24 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n tham d\u1ef1 VCK Asian Cup 2019, AFC \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 4 nh\u00f3m h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i. K\u1ec1 t\u1eeb gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m 2015, c\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c ph\u00e2n chia nh\u00f3m h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng s\u1ebd d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean BXH FIFA th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u1ee7a th\u00e1ng g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng th\u1ea5p l\u00e0 \u0110T Th\u00e1i Lan.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"dt thai lan\" title=\"\u0111t th\u00e1i lan\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/5/28/ngo-lo-viet-nam-sao-dortmund-khen-cau-thu-thai-het-loi.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i Asian Cup 2019</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ec9 n\u1eb1m trong nh\u00f3m 4, \u2018nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa voi chi\u1ebfn\u2019 \u0111ang c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng t\u1eed th\u1ea7n v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng x\u1ee9 ch\u00f9a V\u00e0ng, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch FAT Somyot Poomphan Muang v\u1eabn t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft: \"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng \u0110TQG Th\u00e1i Lan s\u1ebd l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Asian Cup 2019. C\u00e1 nh\u00e2n t\u00f4i mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng r\u1ed3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh 4 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi ng\u00e0y 4.5 t\u1edbi, ch\u00fang ta m\u1edbi bi\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m chia b\u1ea3ng VCK Asian Cup 2019 nh\u01b0ng Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i lo ng\u1ea1i s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u0169 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 nh\u01b0 Australia, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Saudi Arabia v\u00e0 Iraq. <o:p></o:p>B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, FAT ch\u1ec9 \u0111i\u1ec3m danh nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u01b0 Iran, \u00dac, Uzbekistan l\u00e0 hay Jordan, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c... th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng tuy\u1ec7t nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn Vi\u1ec7t Nam (\u0111ang n\u1eb1m \u1edf nh\u00f3m 3).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng khi m\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00edn phong \u0111\u1ed9. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng l\u00e0 1 trong 12 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n c\u00f3 v\u00e9 \u0111i th\u1eb3ng t\u1edbi VCK Asian Cup n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch FAT Somyot Poomphan Muang kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp t\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">VCK Asian Cup s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc T\u00e2y \u00c1 U.A.E v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 1/2019. 12 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n c\u00f3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a 6 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng 4 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t s\u1ebd d\u1eaft tay nhau v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 tham d\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 Confed Cup di\u1ec5n t\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i Qatar v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2021.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-dt-viet-nam-can-cai-thien-nhung-gi-de-tien-xa-tai-vck-asian-cup-2019-168-