:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">PSG vs Monaco l\u00fac 02h05 ng\u00e0y 1/4 (Chung k\u1ebft c\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n Ph\u00e1p League Cup 2017/18): <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><u>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay</u></strong></span></span>, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nhan dinh PSG vs Monaco 02h05 ngay 14 Cup Lien doan Phap hinh anh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh PSG vs Monaco 02h05 ng\u00e0y 14 C\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n Ph\u00e1p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/31/psg-monaco.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">PSG vs Monaco</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh PSG vs Monaco: 1-2</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMonaco \u0111\u00e3 thua trong c\u1ea3 2 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n PSG \u1edf m\u00f9a n\u00e0y c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1-2 t\u1ea1i l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Ligue 1 v\u00e0 Si\u00eau C\u00fap Qu\u1ed1c gia. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y tr\u00f2n 4 th\u00e1ng, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Leonardo Jardim r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPSG s\u1ebd h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Matmut-Atlantique c\u1ee7a Bordeaux cho tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft C\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. Ngo\u00e0i Neymar ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00f9a, Angel Di Maria kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn ra s\u00e2n, Thiago Motta l\u00e3nh \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2, th\u00ec HLV Unai Emery c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Monaco. B\u1ecb \u0111au nh\u1eb9 v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi \u0110T Nga, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Kylian Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u, g\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, tr\u00e1m v\u00e0o ch\u1ed7 tr\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a Neymar v\u00e0 Motta l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 Julian Draxler, Lassana Diarra. D\u00f9 c\u00f4ng khai ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch t\u00e0i c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Emery, nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng v\u00ec hai ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a PSG l\u00e0 Neymar v\u00e0 Di Maria c\u00f9ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. \u1ede h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, c\u1eb7p Yuri Berchiche - Daniel Alves \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Emery y\u00eau th\u00edch h\u01a1n Layvin Kurzawa (\u0111ang xu\u1ed1ng phong \u0111\u1ed9 th\u00ea th\u1ea3m) -Thomas Meunier (kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f2ng Emery). Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, \u0111\u00e2y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a PSG, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi chi\u1ebfc C\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n th\u1ee9 5 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n m\u00ecnh, Monaco r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t b\u00e1t b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Tin r\u1ea5t vui cho C\u0110V Monaco khi HLV Jardim v\u1eeba tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 \u00f4ng r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Louis II v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a. D\u00f9 m\u1ea5t r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t, nh\u01b0ng d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u00e8o l\u00e1i kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf hai s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i: \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 t\u1ea1i Ligue 1, ch\u1ec9 sau ch\u00ednh PSG v\u00e0 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft C\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Jardim c\u0169ng nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh r\u1eb1ng ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd Monaco sung m\u00e3n v\u00e0 \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft nh\u01b0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y. C\u01a1n kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y th\u00e1ng 1/2018 \u0111\u00e3 qua \u0111i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c \u0111ang c\u00f3 chu\u1ed7i 9 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, trong \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh 7 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, khi t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 PSG l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 3 \u1edf m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Monaco (s\u1ebd c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i Parc des Princes v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 17/4 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 Ligue 1) r\u1ea5t h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n, t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ph\u00e1 n\u00e1t gi\u1ea5c m\u1ed9ng \u201c\u0103n ba\u201d c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Emery, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t chu\u1ed7i 5 tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng (4 b\u1ea1i, 1 h\u00f2a) tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN<br>\r\nTheo ch\u00e2u \u00c1, PSG th\u1eafng 9, thua 11 \u1edf 20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t; Monaco th\u1eafng 13, h\u00f2a 1, thua 6 \u1edf 20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\nTr\u00ean s\u00e2n trung l\u1eadp, PSG th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 4 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i, c\u00f2n Monaco thua 3/4 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua. <br>\r\nTheo ch\u00e2u \u00c1, PSG th\u1eafng 5, Monaco th\u1eafng 3 \u1edf 8 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T<br>\r\nL\u1ebb b\u00e0n th\u1eafng<br>\r\nC\u1ea3 4 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i, 7/8 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a PSG v\u00e0 3/4 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Monaco c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0 l\u1ebb. Ngo\u00e0i ra, c\u1ea3 3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n trung l\u1eadp c\u0169ng kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0 l\u1ebb. </div>\r\n<br></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"647","checkdouble":"183199"},{"date":"10:40 31/03","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Bayern Munich vs Dortmund 23h30 ng\u00e0y 31/3 (Bundesliga 2017/18)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u1ee9c","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/31/nhan-dinh-bayern-munich-vs-dortmund-23h30-ngay-313-bundesliga-201718.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}.articlerelate2{padding:6px;min-height:72px}div.articlerelate2>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate2>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate2>a>img{border:0;width:100px;height:68px;float:left;margin-right:6px}div.articlerelate2>span{color:#888}.photolist{background-color:#292929;width:100%;margin:0 auto;padding:8px 0;left:0;text-align:center;position:relative;z-index:1001}.phototopitem{text-align:center}.phototopitem