h Lionel Messi mu\u1ed1n Barca mua David Alaba c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</h2>\r\n<h2>Barca r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay t\u1eeb th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, HLV Ernesto Valverde \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 sung m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u1edf k\u1ef3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-chuyen-nhuong-c187-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng</strong></span> H\u00e8 2018. Vi\u1ec7c Jordi Alba kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi\u1ebfn c\u1ef1u HLV Bilbao kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 y\u00ean t\u00e2m, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1989.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi muon Barca mua David Alaba voi gia khong tuong hinh anh\" title=\"Messi mu\u1ed1n Barca mua David Alaba v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/8/17/Messi-muon-Barca-mua-David-Alaba-voi-gia-khong-tuong-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca c\u1ea7n ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Jordi Alba</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/messi-muon-barca-mua-hau-ve-chelsea-180-182426.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Barca quan t\u00e2m Marcos Alonso</strong></span> c\u1ee7a Chelsea, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ph\u00eda Chelsea kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Barca \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i Luke Shaw c\u1ee7a M.U. Song ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1995 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i \u1edf Premier League, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh. D\u00f9 Barca c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1 cao cho Shaw, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a M.U c\u0169ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Lionel Messi mu\u1ed1n Barca mua David Alaba</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">David Alaba l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Barca. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/barca-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-chieu-mo-sao-bayern-180-182419.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Barca mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Alaba</strong></span> v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 v\u1eeba qua. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao \u1edf c\u1ea3 kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng l\u1eabn ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7. \u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y anh ra s\u00e2n 21 l\u1ea7n \u1edf Bundesliga, ghi 1 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. V\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, anh r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Barca.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi muon Barca mua David Alaba\" title=\"Messi mu\u1ed1n Barca mua David Alaba\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/31/messi-muon-barca-rut-ruot-bayern-munich.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Messi mu\u1ed1n Barca mua David Alaba</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nDiario Gol kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Lionel Messi mu\u1ed1n Barca mua David Alaba c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. M10 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00c1o v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou chi \u0111\u1eadm cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Alaba kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Bayern \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, song kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Barca mua David Alaba th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Bayern Munich \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ebfn 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ea5y l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/real-madrid-29.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Real Madrid</strong></span> c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<